<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/about.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/nav.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
    <title>About Us - AgronomyNet</title>
    <link rel="website icon" type="png"  href="images/logofinal.jpg">

</head>

<body>
   
    <%- include('./partials/nav.ejs') %>  

  
        <section class="about">


            <div class="content">


                <div class="about-image">

                    <img src="/images\about-us img.jpg" alt="About Us Image">


                    <div class="about-overlay">

                    
                        <div class="quotation-box">
                            
                            <div class="quotation-content">

                                <h1>About Us</h1>
                                <p>
                                    AgriHub is a revolutionary online platform designed to foster knowledge sharing, 
                                    community building, and sustainable agriculture. Our mission is to provide a space where farmers,
                                    experts, and agri enthusiasts can come together, exchange ideas,
                                    and drive positive change in the agricultural industry.
                                </p>

                            </div>

                        </div>




                        <div class="about-buttons">

                            <a href="/" class="about-button">Explore AgronomyNet</a>

                        </div>

                    </div>
                
                </div>




                <div class="features-section">


                    <div class="feature-box">

                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                        <h3>Connect with Community</h3>
                        <p>Join our vibrant community of farmers and horticulturists.</p>

                    </div>


                    <div class="feature-box">


                        <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
                        <h3>Agriculture Bot</h3>
                        <p>Utilize our smart agriculture bot for personalized assistance.</p>


                    </div>


                    <div class="feature-box">


                        <i class="fas fa-sun"></i>
                        <h3>Weather and Market Details</h3>
                        <p>Access real-time weather and market information.</p>


                    </div>


                    <div class="feature-box">


                        <i class="fas fa-shopping-basket"></i>
                        <h3>Sell Your Own Produce</h3>
                        <p>List and sell your high-quality produce to a global audience.</p>


                
                    </div>


                </div>


            </div>

            
        </section>




    
    <section class="products">


        <h2>Any One Can Sell Your Produces</h2>

        <div class="product-cards">


            <div class="product-card">

                <img src="/images\about-us veg img.jpg" alt="Product 1">
                <h3>Vegetables</h3>


            </div>


            <div class="product-card">


                <img src="/images\about-us fruit img.jpg" alt="Product 2">
                <h3>Fruits</h3>


            </div>



            <div class="product-card">


                <img src="/images\about-us grains img.jpg" alt="Product 3">
                <h3>Grains</h3>


            </div>


        </div>




        <div class="product-cards">


            <div class="product-card">

                <img src="/images\about-us flower img.jpg" alt="Product 3">
                <h3>Flowers</h3>


            </div>


            <div class="product-card">


                <img src="/images\about-us horticulture img.jpg" alt="Product 3">
                <h3>Green House Produces</h3>


            </div>


            <div class="product-card">

                    
                <img src="/images\about-us greenhouse img.jpg" alt="Product 3">
                <h3>horticulture Produces</h3>

            </div>


        </div>

        
    </section>





    <section class="features">


        <div class="content">



            <div class="feature">


                <h2>Issues we addressed <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i></h2>

                <div class="feature-content">

                    <p>Agriculture faces barriers such as language, literacy, and cost issues, impacting farmers' access to fair pricing and direct selling options.</p>

                </div>


            </div>


            <div class="feature">


                <h2>Solution we give <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i></h2>

                <div class="feature-content">

                    <p>AgronomyNet empowers farmers through direct selling, offers real-time weather and market updates, provides financial assistance, and features an AI-powered AgriChatbot.</p>

                </div>


            </div>



            <div class="feature">


                <h2>Benefits in AgronomyNet <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up"></i></h2>

                <div class="feature-content">

                    <p>AgronomyNet enables fair rates for direct selling, informed decisions through real-time data, financial support, AI-driven assistance, and fosters knowledge-sharing among stakeholders.</p>


                </div>


            </div>



            <div class="feature">


                <h2>Purpose of AgronomyNet <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></h2>

                <div class="feature-content">

                    <p>AgronomyNet aims to drive positive change by overcoming barriers, provide fair trade opportunities, transform agriculture, enhance practices, and make a meaningful impact.</p>

                </div>

            </div>


            <div class="final-statement">

                <p>"Transforming Agriculture with Technology: AgronomyNet fosters fair trade, real-time information, and networking for enhanced practices, making a meaningful impact on the agricultural industry."</p>

            </div>


        </div>


    </section>






    <section class="aim">


        <h2>Our Aim</h2>


        <div class="content">


            <div class="aim-list">


                <div class="aim-item">

                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                    <h3>Empower Farmers</h3>
                    <p>Enable farmers to sell produce at their own rates.</p>

                </div>


                <div class="aim-item">

                    <i class="fas fa-bullhorn"></i>
                    <h3>Marketing Insights</h3>
                    <p>Provide marketing information to enhance farmer knowledge.</p>

                </div>


                <div class="aim-item">

                    <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
                    <h3>Educational Support</h3>
                    <p>Teach effective methods for producing crops.</p>


                </div>



                <div class="aim-item">

                    <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
                    <h3>Global Natural Produce</h3>
                    <p>Promote natural produce consumption worldwide.</p>

                </div>



                <div class="aim-item">

                    <i class="fas fa-shopping-basket"></i>
                    <h3>Direct from Seller</h3>
                    <p>Connect consumers directly with producers.</p>

                </div>


            </div>


        </div>

        
    </section>
    




</body>
</html>